Package jMusicMetaManager

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AnalysisPreferences
    An object of this class holds the settings to be used when jMusicMetaManager analyzes recording metadata.
    AnalysisProcessor
    This class performs the actual processing to detect inconsistencies and redundancies in recording metadata.
    Main
    Runs the jMusicMetaManager software.
    ParseiTunesXMLFileHandler
    An extension of the Xerces XML DefaultHandler class.
    RecordingMetaData
    An object to hold the metadata associated with an MP3 recording that has been added to a music collection.
